# Swift Style

Swift coding conventions for `apps/ios/`. Stub — expand as needed.

## Activation

When editing Swift files in `apps/ios/`.

## Conventions

- Follow Swift API Design Guidelines
- Use Swift 6 concurrency (async/await, Sendable where appropriate)
- Prefer value types; use classes only when reference semantics needed
- Use `@Observable` for ViewModels per agent-ios.mdc

